<h3>Image Tag</h3>

<p>Now, I&rsquo;m going to try the image tag.
<img class="right" src="http://placekitten.com/300/500" width="150" height="250" title="Place Kitten #4" alt="An image of a very cute kitten"></p>

<h3>Block quote</h3>

<p>Another interesting plugin is the Block Quote. You can add a simple quote or tweets, articles,etc. Here we go.</p>

<blockquote><p>Another Interesting reason why our Github Profile matters.</p><footer><strong>@ningsuhen</strong> <cite><a href='https://twitter.com/ningsuhen/status/456334719332790272'>Gramener Rocks</a></cite></footer></blockquote>


