<p><span class='pullquote-right' data-pullquote='We have seen examples of Excerpts, HTML5 Video Tags, Image Tag, Block Quote, Pull Quote.'>
Pull quote allows you to display text without including them in the html markup. One special use case of a pull quote is when you want to repeat the points of a long article. e.g.
