<h3>Gist Tag</h3>

<p>Another feature you will love is the Gist Tag. You can insert a gist by specifying the gist id.</p>

<div><script src='https://gist.github.com/10567944.js?file=0_reuse_code.js'></script>
<noscript><pre><code>// Use Gists to store code you would like to remember later on
console.log(window); // log the &quot;window&quot; object to the console
</code></pre></noscript></div>


<h3>Include Code</h3>

<p>This one allows you to embed code from a file in your system.</p>

